view.name: Approved Link NYC Kiosk Locations
view.description: This dataset lists locations where a LinkNYC kiosk has been approved but is not yet installed.  It includes existing payphones that will be replaced as well as new locations that have been reviewed by community and elected officials.  Although these sites meet all requirements, some of them might not ultimately be built because of issues that may arise during installation.  The dataset is updated weekly.

columns.name: Corner_location
columns.description: The direction the Kiosk is facing.
